        "## Formatting dengan Special Character\n",
        "`\\' = karakter spesial \"escaping nature\"\n",
        "\n",
        "`\\n` = untuk enter\n",
        "\n",
        "`\\` = escaping karakter\n",
        "\n",
        "```python\n",
        "print() = berarti line kosong\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "Tidak boleh ada 2 perintah dalam 1 baris\n",
        "```python\n",
        "print(\"nama depan\") print (\"nama belakang\")\n",
        "```"
      ]
    },
